    <item>
      <title>T-Mobile 移动用户增加，营收超出预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/t-mobile-revenue-beats-estimates-on-more-mobile-subscribers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[T-Mobile US Inc. 报告称，其每月新增手机用户数量超过分析师预期，与同行一样在第二季度吸引了新客户。纽约股市开盘时，该公司股价上涨 3.3%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/t-mobile-revenue-beats-estimates-on-more-mobile-subscribers</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 11:03:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Uber 与比亚迪合作，为其司机提供 10 万辆电动汽车</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/uber-partners-with-byd-on-putting-its-drivers-into-100-000-evs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[优步科技公司 (Uber Technologies Inc.) 将与比亚迪股份有限公司 (BYD Co.) 合作，将 10 万辆电动汽车投入该叫车公司的平台，这是美国和中国企业之间的一项重大交易，值得注意的是，该交易不包括美国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/uber-partners-with-byd-on-putting-its-drivers-into-100-000-evs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>AMD 的人工智能增长推动股价出现 2 月份以来最大涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/amd-delivers-upbeat-sales-forecast-as-it-shifts-into-ai-chips</link>
      <description><![CDATA[芯片制造商超微半导体公司 (Advanced Micro Devices Inc.) 公布了乐观的营收预测，突显出其新型人工智能处理器正在推动增长，其股价一度上涨 11%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/amd-delivers-upbeat-sales-forecast-as-it-shifts-into-ai-chips</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 20:18:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>微软 Azure 增长放缓，考验投资者的耐心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/microsoft-reports-slower-azure-cloud-growth-shares-drop</link>
      <description><![CDATA[微软公司的 Azure 云计算服务季度增长放缓，这对那些急于看到对人工智能产品的巨额投资带来回报的投资者的耐心构成了考验。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/microsoft-reports-slower-azure-cloud-growth-shares-drop</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 20:14:54 GMT</pubDate>
